    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just hard to see them so stressed. i see the look on my daughter's face when she's cleaning up after me or driving me to the doctor. it breaks my heart. i used to be the one who did everything for everyone, and now i'm just another thing on their To-Do list. i just wish i could make it easier for them. i wish i could just... not be a problem anymore.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
